      "side": 1,
      "message": "[🔴 Critical] Line 11: The build downloads ggml-model.bin during pre_build without any checksum or pinned artifact validation, and --no-check-certificate disables TLS certificate verification. This creates a supply-chain risk and makes builds non-reproducible. Pin the model checksum and verify it after download, and remove --no-check-certificate unless there is a documented platform-specific reason.\n```suggestion\n\"wget --quiet --show-progress -O ggml-model.bin https://ggml.ggerganov.com/ggml-model-whisper-base.bin\",\n\"echo \u003csha256\u003e ggml-model.bin | sha256sum -c -\"\n```",
